Cam::

She frowned at Windlord. "Oh no, now it's awake." she said gently 
bouncing the baby bot. "Windlord, I may be a kid, but even I know to 
be quiet around babies."  She shook her head. "I found it in one of 
the rooms. It was alone, and I didn't want to leave it by itself."  
she looked down at the baby. She sighed and looked at 
Windlord. "Here, you want it? my arms are tired."
